<h2 id="about-think">About (think)</h2>

<p>This site was my first attempt to write. I failed miserably and I produced some pretty
crappy content, but I also learned a lot in the process.</p>

<p>These days most of my writing happens at <a href="https://metaredux.com">Meta Redux</a>, but
I still plan to post here things that are worth sharing, but don‚Äôt fit the overall
idea of Meta Redux.</p>

<p>I guess I‚Äôll mostly be writing on programming-related topics, but who knows‚Ä¶
Knowing me there‚Äôs a high chance I won‚Äôt actually write anything at all!</p>

