<p>The comments are powered by the privacy-focused service <a href="https://talk.hyvor.com">Hyvor Talk</a>.
One way to support my work is to sign up for Hyvor via my <a href="https://talk.hyvor.com?aff=14023">affiliate link</a>.</p>

<p>I write all of the articles in Emacs and publish them to GitHub
